@startuml
!include ../proveo.puml

title Proveo theme — session lifecycle

[*]     ARROW_MAIN     Queued
Queued  ARROW_QUEUE    Running  : worker picks up
Running ARROW_CLOUD    Waiting  : awaits LLM
Waiting ARROW_MAIN     Running  : response
Running ARROW_MAIN     Done
Running ARROW_OPTIONAL Paused   : pause
Paused  ARROW_OPTIONAL Running  : resume
Running ARROW_ERROR    Failed   : exception
Done    ARROW_MAIN     [*]
